| Component | Technology |
|---|---|
| Framework | PyTorch |
| Face Detection | MTCNN |
| Visual Model | XceptionNet, EfficientNet |
| Temporal Model | LSTM |
| Audio Model | RawNet2 |
| Explainability | Grad-CAM |
| UI | Streamlit |
